---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { roofingAsphalt, ctaAssistant } from '../../../lib/images';
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AnnouncementBar from '../../../components/AnnouncementBar.astro';
import Navbar from '../../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Hero from '../../../components/Hero.astro';
import LogoSlider from '../../../components/LogoSlider.astro';
import FAQ from '../../../components/FAQ.astro';
import ContactUs from '../../../components/ContactUs.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';

const city = 'Hayward';
const county = 'Alameda County';
const adjective = 'Expert';
---

<Layout
  title={`${adjective} ADU Contractors in ${city}, CA | Hamilton Exteriors`}
  description={`Hamilton Exteriors provides ${adjective.toLowerCase()} ADU contractors in ${city}, CA. Expert design, permits, and construction. Call for a free consultation!`}
>
  <AnnouncementBar />
  <Navbar />
  <Hero
    formTitle={`Get a FREE Estimate in ${city}`}
    headline={`${adjective} ADU Contractors in ${city}, CA`}
  />
  <LogoSlider />

  <!-- Why Choose Section -->
  <section class="w-full bg-white py-12 md:py-32 lg:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="hidden lg:block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <Image src={roofingAsphalt} alt="Hamilton Exteriors ADU project" width={1200} height={900} class="w-full h-auto object-cover" style="aspect-ratio: 632/478;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div>
      <h2 style="font-family: 'THE BOLD FONT (FREE VERSION)', 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Why Choose Hamilton Exteriors as Your {adjective} ADU Contractors in {city}, CA?
      </h2>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Skilled. Dependable. Proven.
      </h3>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Hamilton Exteriors provides expert ADU contractors in Hayward, CA with deep knowledge of this centrally located East Bay city. Hayward's mix of single-family homes in neighborhoods like Hayward Hills, Tennyson, and Southgate offers excellent opportunities for ADU construction, and our team brings the expertise needed to turn your backyard or garage into valuable living space.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Our expert approach covers the full scope of ADU development. We start with a thorough property assessment, create detailed architectural plans that comply with Hayward's municipal code, manage all permit applications, and execute construction with skilled tradespeople who take pride in their craft. Every decision is backed by years of ADU building experience in the East Bay.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        From foundation to finish, we apply expert-level attention to structural integrity, plumbing, electrical, and interior finishes that make your ADU feel like a true home rather than an afterthought.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Local Expertise</strong> — Deep knowledge of local zoning regulations and building codes ensures your ADU project moves through permitting smoothly and efficiently.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Full-Service Build</strong> — From architectural design and engineering through foundation work, framing, and finish carpentry — all under one roof with a single point of contact.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Quality Assurance</strong> — Every build meets the highest construction standards with thorough inspections at every phase, ensuring quality from foundation to finish.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">On-Time Delivery</strong> — We build realistic schedules and stick to them, keeping your ADU project moving forward without the drawn-out timelines that plague unreliable contractors.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why ADU Contractors Section -->
  <section class="w-full bg-cream py-12 md:py-32 lg:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div>
      <h2 style="font-family: 'THE BOLD FONT (FREE VERSION)', 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Why {adjective} ADU Contractors in {city}, CA Are Essential?
      </h2>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Space. Growth. Reliability.
      </h3>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Hayward sits at the geographic heart of the East Bay with easy access to both San Francisco and Silicon Valley, making it an increasingly popular city for families and professionals. As housing costs continue to climb across the region, ADUs provide Hayward homeowners with a practical solution for multigenerational living, home office space, or supplemental rental income.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Expert contractors are essential in Hayward because the city's varied terrain — from flatland lots near downtown to hillside properties along the eastern hills — presents different construction challenges that require specialized knowledge. Foundation requirements, drainage planning, and utility hookups vary significantly depending on where your property sits, and mistakes in these areas lead to expensive fixes down the road.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
        Working with expert ADU contractors ensures your project is built right the first time, with proper engineering, quality materials, and construction techniques that protect your investment and deliver a space your family can rely on for decades.
      </p>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden lg:block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <Image src={ctaAssistant} alt="Hamilton Exteriors construction crew" width={1200} height={900} class="w-full h-auto object-cover" style="aspect-ratio: 632/626;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <FAQ />
  <ContactUs />
  <Footer />
</Layout>
